import React from 'react'; const Welcome = ({ onD3React, onQGIS, onFinish }) => { return (

WELCOME!

You are going to evaluate the data visualization between the static map, created by QGIS, and the interactive map, created by D3.js with React.

The data visualization is about travel experience with different transportation modes.



You can find the data regarding HRV, HR_mad, Stress, and satisfaction score during the travel.

You need to try yourself to gain the information as much as you can. There is no limited time on it.

You can choose the button which map you want to explore, and you can click the "back button" to change your preference.



If you think you are done, you can click the "finish" button to answer the questionnaire.



Once you click finish, you cannot go back again.

); }; export default Welcome;
